http_applications_v2.title: Version Management
http_applications_v2.description: Manage Versions and Environments to safely control configuration changes
http_applications_v2.empty_state.descrip: Manage configurations on the edge with versioning, staging, and rollbacks
http_applications_v2.empty_state.detail_: Create independent configurations to make changes with no risk of impacting live traffic
Safely deploy changes to test and pre production environments ahead of deploying to production
Quickly rollback deployed changes when issues occur
